                                <span>COMMUNITY ENGAGEMENT</span>
                            </h3>
                            <p>A key aspect of the IB programmes is community engagement. From the Primary Years to the Diploma and Career-related Programmes, students explore, understand, and actively contribute to their communities through various initiatives.</p>
