                                            <article>
                                                                                                    <div class="content">
                                                        <p class="description">I think the best part of learning in DC is the open minded approach the school has about different concepts of learning. New ideas are allowed to be explored during classes but the crucial part is allowing these ideas to flourish beyond class.</p>
